title: TRANSPORT MINISTER KHAW BOON WAN SPOTTED ON CIRCLE LINE MRT DURING MORNING PEAK HOUR?
text:
TRANSPORT MINISTER KHAW BOON WAN SPOTTED ON CIRCLE LINE MRT DURING MORNING PEAK HOUR?   Advertisement 
Dear Editors, 
I was on the Circle Line travelling towards HabourFront at about 9am when I spotted a man who looked like Transport Minister Khaw Boon Wan on the train. 
Nobody seemed to notice him and he was just observing his surroundings. When i alighted at Buona Vista MRT, he was still on the MRT. Minister Khaw sure take his job seriously... 
Aswin A.S.S. Contributor Editor's Note:
